This is a simple Flask application that provides a RESTful API to manage a collection of books stored in an SQLite database. The API supports basic CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) operations.

Prerequisites

- Python 3.x
- Flask
- Dataset (Python package)

Installation

1. Clone the repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/yourusername/flask-book-api.git
   cd flask-book-api
   ```

2. Create a virtual environment and activate it:
   ```bash
   python -m venv venv
   source venv/bin/activate  # On Windows use `venv\Scripts\activate`
   ```

3. Install the required packages
